<br>
This body is designed to give those who wish to see the ideals of wizardry upheld a chance to speak out, without thought given to diety or race. It will also be capable of delivering justice when it is needed, but only, ONLY in times of dire need and when it is cleary shown that there is no other way. We have no wish to rule Norrath, only to make sure that all sides be heard, and those who wish to be heard have the chance to speak without fear of retribution.<br>
<br>
Honorary members are Aurianne, Shazzbot (if they wish it), and myself, and any erudites who do not hold with your movement.  <p><img src="http://64.3.126.108/webadmin/imagespages/panel127426.JPG"><BR>
